trans-unit.source: Represents the resource key for the <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 代表的資源索引鍵<xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplateKey"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplateKey"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: When constructed without a data type, you must specify `DataType` as a property.
trans-unit.target: 當建構沒有資料類型，您必須指定`DataType`做為屬性。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplateKey"></xref> class with the specified type.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplateKey"></xref>具有指定之類型的類別。

trans-unit.source: The type for which this template is designed.

This is either a <xref:System.Type> (to indicate that the <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref> is used to display items of the given type), or a string (to indicate that the <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref> is used to display <xref href="System.Xml.XmlNode"></xref> elements with the given tag name).
trans-unit.target: 這可能是<xref:System.Type>(表示<xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref>用來顯示給定類型的項目)，或字串 (表示<xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref>用來顯示<xref href="System.Xml.XmlNode"></xref>指定的標記名稱的項目)。</xref:System.Type>
